177
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Iz priča ću priču, nećemo ići redak po redak.

178
00:20:19,599 --> 00:20:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo se dogodilo.

179
00:20:22,599 --> 00:20:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi nam čovjek koji je slijep od svog rođenja.

180
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] I Isus sa svojim učenicima prolazi kroz taj grad.

181
00:20:40,599 --> 00:20:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] i učenici kažu, pogledajte tog sirotog čovjeka.

182
00:20:46,599 --> 00:20:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] je li slijep zbog svog grijeha ili grijeha svojih roditelja?

183
00:20:56,599 --> 00:21:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] jer mnogo puta u židovskoj kulturi,

184
00:21:04,599 --> 00:21:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] ako se osobi dogodi nešto jako loše,

185
00:21:10,599 --> 00:21:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti da ih Bog kažnjava zbog njihovog grijeha.

186
00:21:16,599 --> 00:21:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže, nije ni do njegovih roditelja,

187
00:21:24,599 --> 00:21:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] nije ni do njega.

188
00:21:26,599 --> 00:21:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Slušajte ovaj redak.

189
00:21:29,599 --> 00:21:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo nije kazna.

190
00:21:33,599 --> 00:21:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je da bi se Bog proslavio.

191
00:21:39,599 --> 00:21:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] i braćom molim vas da zadržite,

192
00:21:46,599 --> 00:21:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] da čvrsto držite taj redak.

193
00:21:49,599 --> 00:21:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sa mnoštom nas ovdje u sobi već raz,

194
00:21:54,599 --> 00:22:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da postoje neki od nas

195
00:22:01,599 --> 00:22:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji prolaze kroz teške trenutke i teške razdoblje u životu.

196
00:22:04,599 --> 00:22:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] I svi mi u jednom trenutku se zapitamo:

197
00:22:11,599 --> 00:22:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, zašto?

198
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ili kažemo: Ovo je moja krivica.

199
00:22:18,599 --> 00:22:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam glup.

200
00:22:21,599 --> 00:22:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] Učinio sam nešto krivo.

201
00:22:24,599 --> 00:22:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] Zaslužujem ovo.

202
00:22:27,599 --> 00:22:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što Isus kaže?

203
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je za veću slavu Božju.

204
00:22:37,599 --> 00:22:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad pozivam vas da izaberete vjerovati u to.

205
00:22:47,599 --> 00:22:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Pavo nam kaže:

206
00:22:52,599 --> 00:23:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo da Bog izvodi na dobro sve stvari

207
00:23:00,599 --> 00:23:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji ga ljube.

208
00:23:03,599 --> 00:23:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Što god prolazili u ovom trenutku u životu,

209
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] Neki imamo male probleme.

210
00:23:14,599 --> 00:23:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Neki od nas prolaze kroz katastrofe.

211
00:23:19,599 --> 00:23:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bar tokom ovog vikenda držite se za taj redak.

212
00:23:29,599 --> 00:23:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog te ne kažnjava.

213
00:23:31,599 --> 00:23:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog te ne kažnjava.

214
00:23:33,599 --> 00:23:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Iskoristit će tvoju katastrofu za svoju proslavu.

215
00:23:41,599 --> 00:23:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] Please hold on to that.

216
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Please.

217
00:23:44,599 --> 00:23:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te, drži se toga.

218
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] Isus dolazi u susret sa osobom.

219
00:23:53,599 --> 00:24:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] I doslovno uzme plato i namaže mu na oči.

220
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] I mislim da sam ja slijepac.

221
00:24:04,599 --> 00:24:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] I da mi neko dođe i namaže blato na oči.

222
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao bih mu: Već sam slijep, ne moraš pogoršavati.

223
00:24:17,599 --> 00:24:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gdje vidimo neko ko radi nešto sa blatom u Starom Zavijetu?

224
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je načinio nas od blata.

225
00:24:34,599 --> 00:24:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže da je Bog uzeo zemlju i oblikao nas.

226
00:24:42,599 --> 00:24:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] I udahnuo svoj dah u nas.

227
00:24:47,599 --> 00:24:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] I počeli smo živjeti.

228
00:24:50,599 --> 00:25:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] Činjenica da Bog radi i Krist radi s blatom na čovjeku.

229
00:25:02,599 --> 00:25:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] Radi kreativni rad.

230
00:25:07,599 --> 00:25:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se, ovaj čovjek je slijep od rođenja.

231
00:25:12,599 --> 00:25:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Iisus ne samo da popravlja problem.

232
00:25:19,599 --> 00:25:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Donosi jednu potpuno novu realnost u njegov život.

233
00:25:26,599 --> 00:25:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Možda postoje vremena u tvom životu

234
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] kad se osjećaš kao da Bog trja blato po tebi.

235
00:25:40,599 --> 00:25:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] i kažeš:

236
00:25:41,599 --> 00:25:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Bože molim te nemoji činiti da bude još gore."

237
00:25:48,599 --> 00:25:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Već je dovoljno loše i ovako.

238
00:25:52,599 --> 00:25:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali Isus koji je gospodin

239
00:25:57,599 --> 00:26:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne želi samo popraviti te.

240
00:26:03,599 --> 00:26:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] Želi stvoriti nove stvari u tvojom životu.

241
00:26:09,599 --> 00:26:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] i on kaže:

242
00:26:11,599 --> 00:26:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Moram činiti dijela očeva."

243
00:26:16,599 --> 00:26:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se koliko smo bili svjesni

244
00:26:28,599 --> 00:26:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] Božje ljubavi prošle godine, očeve ljubavi.

245
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] Otac je taj koji šalje Isusa

246
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] kao gospodina

247
00:26:41,599 --> 00:26:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] sva moć i sva autoritet

248
00:26:45,599 --> 00:26:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] da bi rekreirao različite dijelove tvojom života.

249
00:26:53,599 --> 00:26:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] I moram nešto reći.

250
00:26:57,599 --> 00:27:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Budući da je Krist gospodin

251
00:27:03,599 --> 00:27:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne postoji jedan muškarac u ovoj sobi večeras

252
00:27:10,599 --> 00:27:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji je izvan nade, za kojeg nema nade.

253
00:27:15,599 --> 00:27:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira koliko je slomljen

254
00:27:20,599 --> 00:27:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira koliko je tvoja tama tamna

255
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj čovjek te može ponovno stvoriti.

256
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Pavao kaže:

257
00:27:34,599 --> 00:27:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Ako je bilo koji čovjek u Hristu,

258
00:27:41,599 --> 00:27:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] on je novo stvorenje.

259
00:27:45,599 --> 00:27:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Stare stvari su prošle.

260
00:27:49,599 --> 00:27:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] sve je novo."

261
00:27:51,599 --> 00:27:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je novo.

262
00:27:52,599 --> 00:28:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Je došao nama ovog vikenda

263
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] da bi učinio sve stvari novima u našem životu.

264
00:28:10,599 --> 00:28:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] došao je ovdje da ozdravi,

265
00:28:15,599 --> 00:28:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovdje obnoviti,

266
00:28:19,599 --> 00:28:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] i došao je ovdje stvoriti nove stvari u tvojom životu.

267
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne želim biti dramatičan.

268
00:28:33,599 --> 00:28:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne pokušavam širiti pozitivnu energiju.

269
00:28:39,599 --> 00:28:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je istina o gospodstvu Isuse Krista.

270
00:28:46,599 --> 00:28:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] I neka vam Bog da milost ovog trenutka

271
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] da povjerujete u te riječi.

272
00:28:56,599 --> 00:29:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek je u stvari ozdravljeno.

273
00:29:02,599 --> 00:29:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek po prvi put u životu ima vid.

274
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Već je odrasla osoba u tom trenutku.

275
00:29:16,599 --> 00:29:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Slijep je cijelog života.

276
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] I ne mislite li da mi nekad u svom životu jednostavno odustanemo?

277
00:29:28,599 --> 00:29:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mučimo se sa određenim grijehom.

278
00:29:32,599 --> 00:29:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo naklonost da imamo loš karakter ili loše nagone.

279
00:29:39,599 --> 00:29:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] Malo volimo previše popit.

280
00:29:43,599 --> 00:29:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] I u jednom trenutku svi kažemo:

281
00:29:48,599 --> 00:29:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Dobro, takav sam."

282
00:29:53,599 --> 00:29:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pokušao sam, ali ništa se ne može učiniti.

283
00:29:58,599 --> 00:30:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da, nešto se može učiniti.

284
00:30:02,599 --> 00:30:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] I njegovo ime je Isus.

285
00:30:06,599 --> 00:30:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] On može učiniti sve.

286
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je godina ovaj čovjek žudio za time da bude ozdravljen?

287
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mislite li možda da kad je imao deset godine da je razmišljao, možda ću idući tjedan?

288
00:30:29,599 --> 00:30:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mislite li možda da je petnaest razmišljao, a možda kad budem imao dvadeset ću vidjeti?

289
00:30:40,599 --> 00:30:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da je 35, mislio da je dalje moguće?

290
00:30:48,599 --> 00:30:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno je došao do toga da je prihvatio, samo prihvatio.

291
00:30:54,599 --> 00:31:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je Isus gospodin uhodao u njegov svijet.

292
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sada čovjek može vidjeti.

293
00:31:07,599 --> 00:31:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje postaje malo smiješno.

294
00:31:10,599 --> 00:31:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje postaje malo smiješno.

295
00:31:12,599 --> 00:31:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] I od jedan put taj čovjek koji je cijelo vrijeme sjedio i prosio,

296
00:31:25,599 --> 00:31:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] od jedan put je aktivan i ide okolo i govor i mogu vidjeti, mogu vidjeti.

297
00:31:29,599 --> 00:31:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] I svi gledaju njega.

298
00:31:32,599 --> 00:31:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne bi taj lik trebao biti slijep?

299
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] Slijep je već 37 godina.

300
00:31:42,599 --> 00:31:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Što to nije on?

301
00:31:45,599 --> 00:31:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bi rekli, mislim da nije.

302
00:31:49,599 --> 00:31:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izgleda kao on.

303
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj čovjek je slijep, ovaj vidi.

304
00:31:57,599 --> 00:32:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on govori, ne ne, to sam ja, to sam ja, nisam prije vidio, ali sad vidim, vidim.

305
00:32:07,599 --> 00:32:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] Stvorio je takvu pomamo.

306
00:32:13,599 --> 00:32:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da su ga odveli do starješina.

307
00:32:18,599 --> 00:32:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kreće ispitivanje.

308
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sada će velika razprava.

309
00:32:24,599 --> 00:32:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad počinje velika razprava, je li to isti čovjek, je li to on, što se točno događa?

310
00:32:34,599 --> 00:32:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju starješine napokon pitaju samog čovjeka, što se dogodilo?

311
00:32:45,599 --> 00:32:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi ovo mogao objasniti?

312
00:32:49,599 --> 00:32:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on im kaže:

313
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Jesus rubbed mud on my eyes and told me to wash, I did, and now I can see."

314
00:32:58,599 --> 00:33:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je namazao blato na moje oči, rekao mi da odem to oprat, i sad vidim.

315
00:33:03,599 --> 00:33:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] I svi se počinju svađati.

316
00:33:07,599 --> 00:33:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] tada mu kažu:

317
00:33:11,599 --> 00:33:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] "Who do you think this guy is?"

318
00:33:16,599 --> 00:33:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže:

319
00:33:18,599 --> 00:33:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] "To je prorok."

320
00:33:21,599 --> 00:33:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] A starješine mu kaže:

321
00:33:25,599 --> 00:33:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] "He can't be a prophet."

322
00:33:28,599 --> 00:33:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] On liječi subotom.

323
00:33:32,599 --> 00:33:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Govori neke radikalne stvari.

324
00:33:36,599 --> 00:33:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] On nije prorok.

325
00:33:39,599 --> 00:33:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] I slijepac počinje branići Isusa.

326
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako možete reći da nije prorok?

327
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bio slijep i sad vidim.

328
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad vidim.

329
00:33:57,599 --> 00:34:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nobody except a servant of God can do that.

330
00:34:00,599 --> 00:34:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko osim Božijeg sluge to ne može učiniti.

331
00:34:03,599 --> 00:34:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] So the elders switch tactics.

332
00:34:07,599 --> 00:34:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] I starješine mijenjaju taktiku.

333
00:34:09,599 --> 00:34:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] And they get his parents to come in.

334
00:34:11,599 --> 00:34:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] I pozovu njegove roditelje da i oni dođu.

335
00:34:14,599 --> 00:34:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Is this your boy?

336
00:34:16,599 --> 00:34:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Yeah, that's our son.

337
00:34:18,599 --> 00:34:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je naš sin.

338
00:34:20,599 --> 00:34:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to da sad može vidjeti?

339
00:34:23,599 --> 00:34:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] We don't know.

340
00:34:25,599 --> 00:34:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo.

341
00:34:26,599 --> 00:34:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] On nije naš sin, ali mi ne znamo što se dogodilo.

342
00:34:32,599 --> 00:34:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pričajte s njim, he's old enough.

343
00:34:35,599 --> 00:34:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] We're out of here, talk to him.

344
00:34:39,599 --> 00:34:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ćemo da ovdje pričajte s njim.

345
00:34:41,599 --> 00:34:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Now it's interesting, John makes a comment.

346
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimljivo je da Ivan tu dodaje komentar.

347
00:34:47,599 --> 00:34:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] And here's what John says.

348
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo Ivan kaže.

349
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] The parents answered this way.

350
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Roditelji su tako odgovorili.

351
00:34:54,599 --> 00:34:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] Because they didn't want to get in trouble.

352
00:34:57,599 --> 00:34:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nisu htjeli doći u nevolju.

353
00:34:59,599 --> 00:35:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] The Jewish leadership hated Jesus so much.

354
00:35:02,599 --> 00:35:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vođe židovske su toliko mrzile Isusa.

355
00:35:06,599 --> 00:35:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] That if you spoke positively about Jesus.

356
00:35:10,599 --> 00:35:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] You get thrown out of the temple.

357
00:35:12,599 --> 00:35:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ako ste pozitivno pričali o njemu.

358
00:35:15,599 --> 00:35:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izbacile bi vas iz sinagoge.

359
00:35:17,599 --> 00:35:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] You would be ostracized.

360
00:35:19,599 --> 00:35:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bili bi on doslovno odbačeni.

361
00:35:22,599 --> 00:35:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izbačeni iz društva.

362
00:35:24,599 --> 00:35:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovi ste.

363
00:35:26,599 --> 00:35:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže.

364
00:35:28,599 --> 00:35:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] The parents were more afraid of the leaders.

365
00:35:37,599 --> 00:35:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Than they were willing to talk about Jesus.

366
00:35:41,599 --> 00:35:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] So they just walk away back into safety.

367
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] So they bring the boy back in.

368
00:35:50,599 --> 00:35:54,599
